<h3 id="site-1-la-torre-scenic-viewpoint">Site 1: La Torre scenic viewpoint</h3>

<p>The highest point of the mountain range (4009 m.a.s.l.).</p>

<p>Composed of a coffee shop, a panoramic viewpoint platform with an interpretation module, parking space, a stable, and hiking trails.</p>

