<h3 id="site-2-laguna-los-ordoÃ±ez-geological-and-biological-viewpoint">Site 2: Laguna los OrdoÃ±ez geological and biological viewpoint</h3>

<p>The most fragile site. Composed of observation decks without railing and defined trails to preserve the fragile soil surface and vegetation, an interpretation module, and an area for services containing parking space, a stable, and dry toilets.</p>

