<hr />

<h3 id="site-3-puerta-del-cielo-scenic-viewpoint">Site 3: Puerta del Cielo scenic viewpoint</h3>

<p>Two abandoned structures containing partial floors made of stone from an old house are reconditioned to contain panoramic viewpoint platforms with interpretation modules and dry toilets. Accessible by foot or on horseback from the main regional ecotourism centre (ca. 2 km).</p>

